Scorponok walked into the Predacon Cavern. He noticed Dark Mouse,
"Hey 
Dark Mouse." He also noticed QuickStrike. "Hey." He then started 
talking to both of them. "I'm back. Sorry I was long but when I got 
back to the Predacon ship, I found that my room was underattack. Well 
anyway, if you dont need me, I'll be getting my lab up and running." 
With this Scorponok started to walkto his lab. "Ohhh and hows the
base 
going?"
